
### to run the project do:

1. set WORKDIR in dockerfile to be the project root directory - for example /etc/codes_project
2. do cd into project root directory codes_project
3. run - docker-compose up
4. Access the service:
    http://{Host}:{Port}/predict?text={Text}&patient_id={patient_id}
5. response format:
{"code":{predicted code - string},"is_new_patient":{bool},"patient_id":{string},"text":string}
